  <brief_title>Study of Preoperative Management of Angiotensin Converting Enzyme Inhibitor (ACEi) and Angiotensin Receptor Blocker (ARB) Medications</brief_title>
  <acronym>PASS</acronym>
  <official_title>Pre-Operative Inhibition of the Angiotensin System Study: A Prospective Randomized Single-Blinded Trial of Pre-Operative Management of Medications That Inhibit the Renin-Angiotensin System</official_title>
  <sponsors>
